songs.title: I’m Fine (Demo)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
I'm fine
Fine, I'm fine
Fine, I'm fine yeah
Fine, I'm fine, yeah, I'm fine

[Chorus]
Yeah, I'm fine
Don't be worried 'bout me, my nigga, I'm fine
Feel like what my bitch look like, I'm fine (Straight up, straight up)
I just wanna have the time of my life (Yeah)
I'm fine (Ooh-ooh)
Don't be worried 'bout me, my nigga, I'm fine
Feel like what my bitch look like (Yeah), I'm fine (Ooh-ooh)
I just wanna have the time of my life (Straight up)

[Post-Chorus]
I don't really (Yah), I don't really care if a nigga don't like me (Yah, yah)
Other than a wife, I got everything I need (Everything I need)
A house in the hills I'm finna go buy me (Ooh-ooh)
Plenty more Y-3 (Ooh-ooh), hatin' ass niggas ain't got cheese

[Open Instrumental]
Ooh-ooh
Ooh, ooh
Ooh, ooh
Ooh-agh, yup
